# Demo Builder Output — AgriPro Operations Console

## Status: COMPLETE

Hero features implemented and building:
- **Role-based login** (4 roles: Procurement, Quality, Warehouse, Management) with scoped nav and permissions
- **Inspections tab** with full search/filter, stage pipeline, AI OCR cert scanning (Tesseract.js), anomaly detection (moisture, aflatoxin, vomitoxin, test weight flagging), and inline approval controls
- **Procurement Board** with campaign cards, approval workflows, and volume tracking
- **Role-scoped Dashboards** with Recharts (bar/pie/line), PDF export (jsPDF), Excel export (xlsx)
- **Documents**, **Warehouse**, **Audit Log**, **Notifications** (bell + tray), and **Admin** (management-only)
- IBM Plex Sans/Mono fonts; agricultural green/blue palette; no em/en dashes

