## handoff
- **Produced**: `public/demos/agripro/` (built), `public/work-samples/agripro.png` (screenshot), `workSamples.js` entry (id 20)
- **Decisions**: frontend-only with Tesseract.js client-side OCR and realistic mock data; no Flask backend needed
- **Next needs**: deploy step should push `michaelwegter.com` to main; no mw-backend changes
- **Risks**: Tesseract.js WASM loads from CDN at runtime (~5s first OCR scan); chunk sizes large (624 kB) but within acceptable range for demo; live Tesseract OCR depends on CDN availability
